highlights.text: “Love Is Gone (with JOSHUA of SEVENTEEN)” by SLANDER, SEVENTEEN, and JOSHUA is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Japan, up 27 spots at #69.
“BON” by Number_i has been on Viral Songs Japan the longest, at 434 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Japan. “Golden” is the highest at #5.
